-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>🚥 Pre-merge checks | ✅ 4</summary>\n\n<details>\n<summary>✅ Passed checks (4 passed)</summary>\n\n|               Check name              | Status   | Explanation                                                                                                                                                                                                      |\n| :-----------------------------------: | :------- | :--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|              Title check              | ✅ Passed | The title accurately describes the main change: fixing a tag association screen gap after keyboard dismiss on Android, which is the primary focus of the changeset.                                              |\n|           Description check           | ✅ Passed | The description clearly relates to the changeset, explaining the problem (bottom gap in tag association modal), root cause (absoluteFill preventing resize), and the fix (removing absoluteFill, using flex: 1). |\n|           Docstring Coverage          | ✅ Passed | No functions found in the changed files to evaluate docstring coverage. Skipping docstring coverage check.                                                                                                       |\n| Pr Description Must Follow Guidelines | ✅ Passed | PR description includes problem statement, root cause analysis, solution explanation, and test plan verification steps as required.                                                                              |\n\n</details>\n\n<sub>✏️ Tip: You can configure your own custom pre-merge checks in the settings.</sub>\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_end -->\n\n<!-- finishing_touch_checkbox_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>✨ Finishing Touches